---
title: Agent Fan-Out — Phase 2 (Parallel Execution, 6 Agents)
---
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber

    participant ORC as Orchestrator<br/>(Temporal Workflow)
    participant TEMPORAL as Temporal
    participant REDIS as Redis Streams
    participant CR as claimreview-matcher<br/>(Temporal Worker)
    participant CL as coverage-left<br/>(Temporal Worker)
    participant CC as coverage-center<br/>(Temporal Worker)
    participant CRR as coverage-right<br/>(Temporal Worker)
    participant DE as domain-evidence<br/>(Temporal Worker)
    participant SV as source-validator<br/>(Temporal Worker)
    participant GFCT as Google Fact Check<br/>Tools API
    participant NEWS as NewsAPI / GNews
    participant MBFC as Media Bias<br/>Fact Check
    participant PRIMARY as CDC / WHO /<br/>SEC / Courts

    Note over ORC,PRIMARY: Precondition: entity-extractor STOP received (Phase 1 complete).<br/>Orchestrator dispatches all 6 agents simultaneously via Temporal.

    par Parallel Temporal activity dispatch (Promise.all)
        ORC->>TEMPORAL: schedule activity: claimreview-matcher<br/>({run_id, claim_normalized, entities})
        TEMPORAL->>CR: execute activity
    and
        ORC->>TEMPORAL: schedule activity: coverage-left<br/>({run_id, claim_text, entities})
        TEMPORAL->>CL: execute activity
    and
        ORC->>TEMPORAL: schedule activity: coverage-center<br/>({run_id, claim_text, entities})
        TEMPORAL->>CC: execute activity
    and
        ORC->>TEMPORAL: schedule activity: coverage-right<br/>({run_id, claim_text, entities})
        TEMPORAL->>CRR: execute activity
    and
        ORC->>TEMPORAL: schedule activity: domain-evidence<br/>({run_id, claim_text, entities, domain})
        TEMPORAL->>DE: execute activity
    and
        ORC->>TEMPORAL: schedule activity: source-validator<br/>({run_id, claim_text, entities})
        TEMPORAL->>SV: execute activity
    end

    Note over CR,GFCT: ClaimReview Matcher (independent)

    CR->>REDIS: XADD ... type=START phase=fanout
    CR->>GFCT: GET /factcheck/v1alpha1/claims:search<br/>?query=claim_normalized
    GFCT-->>CR: ClaimReview results[]

    CR->>CR: compute semantic match score<br/>select best match if score >= 0.75

    CR->>REDIS: XADD ... type=OBS<br/>publish(CLAIMREVIEW_MATCH, F)<br/>publish(CLAIMREVIEW_VERDICT, F)<br/>publish(CLAIMREVIEW_SOURCE, F)<br/>publish(CLAIMREVIEW_MATCH_SCORE, F)
    CR->>REDIS: XADD progress:...:run_id *<br/>agent=claimreview-matcher event=observations_published
    CR->>REDIS: XADD ... type=STOP finalStatus=F
    CR-->>TEMPORAL: activity complete

    Note over CL,MBFC: Coverage Left (same pattern for Center + Right)

    CL->>REDIS: XADD ... type=START phase=fanout
    CL->>NEWS: GET articles?q=entities&from=source_date<br/>filter: left-spectrum outlets
    NEWS-->>CL: articles[]

    CL->>MBFC: GET bias ratings for outlet names
    MBFC-->>CL: bias_scores[]

    CL->>CL: analyze framing across article set<br/>select top credibility source

    CL->>REDIS: XADD ... type=OBS<br/>publish(COVERAGE_ARTICLE_COUNT, F)<br/>publish(COVERAGE_FRAMING, F)<br/>publish(COVERAGE_TOP_SOURCE, F)<br/>publish(COVERAGE_TOP_SOURCE_URL, F)
    CL->>REDIS: XADD progress:...:run_id *<br/>agent=coverage-left event=observations_published
    CL->>REDIS: XADD ... type=STOP finalStatus=F
    CL-->>TEMPORAL: activity complete

    Note over CC: Coverage Center — same flow as Coverage Left
    CC->>REDIS: START -> OBS -> STOP
    CC-->>TEMPORAL: activity complete

    Note over CRR: Coverage Right — same flow as Coverage Left
    CRR->>REDIS: START -> OBS -> STOP
    CRR-->>TEMPORAL: activity complete

    Note over DE,PRIMARY: Domain Evidence (independent)

    DE->>REDIS: XADD ... type=START phase=fanout
    DE->>DE: determine relevant primary source<br/>from CLAIM_DOMAIN and entities

    DE->>PRIMARY: fetch authoritative source document
    PRIMARY-->>DE: source content

    DE->>DE: evaluate alignment between<br/>source content and claim

    DE->>REDIS: XADD ... type=OBS<br/>publish(DOMAIN_SOURCE_NAME, F)<br/>publish(DOMAIN_SOURCE_URL, F)<br/>publish(DOMAIN_EVIDENCE_ALIGNMENT, F)<br/>publish(DOMAIN_CONFIDENCE, F)
    DE->>REDIS: XADD progress:...:run_id *<br/>agent=domain-evidence event=observations_published
    DE->>REDIS: XADD ... type=STOP finalStatus=F
    DE-->>TEMPORAL: activity complete

    Note over SV: Source Validator (independent)

    SV->>REDIS: XADD ... type=START phase=fanout
    SV->>SV: extract links,<br/>validate URLs,<br/>compute source convergence,<br/>aggregate citations
    SV->>REDIS: XADD ... type=OBS<br/>publish(SOURCE_EXTRACTED_URL, F)<br/>publish(SOURCE_VALIDATION_STATUS, F)<br/>publish(SOURCE_CONVERGENCE_SCORE, F)<br/>publish(CITATION_LIST, F)
    SV->>REDIS: XADD progress:...:run_id *<br/>agent=source-validator event=observations_published
    SV->>REDIS: XADD ... type=STOP finalStatus=F
    SV-->>TEMPORAL: activity complete

    Note over ORC: Orchestrator receives 6 STOP messages<br/>via XREADGROUP. Completion register: 6/6.<br/>Dispatches blindspot-detector (Phase 3a).
